data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bed, 2 bath home! This cozy abode offers a comfortable and inviting atmosphere for you and your loved ones. With three spacious bedrooms, there's plenty of room for everyone to have their own space. The two bathrooms ensure convenience and privacy for all. The home's layout is thoughtfully designed, providing a seamless flow between the living areas. The kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with ample counter space. The deck is perfect for outdoor gatherings or simply enjoying some fresh air. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home sweet home!
